data.meta_description: Groove Collective specialise in weddings and large corporate and social events. They will work with you well before your event date to understand your preferences and plan just the right music for your celebration.
data.text:
Groove Collective is a collection of very talented musicians: Hayli - one fabulous lead singer, the smooth sound of Tony, Craig - a guitar god, Chad - piano virtuoso, Danny - drum legend and Kelly - our funky bass lady. Funk, pop, soul and R&B - Groove Collective do it all!

Groove Collective specialise in weddings and large corporate and social events. They will work with you well before your event date to understand your preferences and plan just the right music for your celebration.

We believe our customers needs are of the utmost importance. Our entire band is committed to meeting those needs. As a result, a high percentage of our business is from repeat customers and referrals. We would welcome the opportunity to deliver you the best service in the industry.
